# Auth API 테스트

### 회원가입 요청 - 손님
# @no-redirect
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginType": "EMAIL",
  "email": "guestexample.com",
  "name": "홍길동",
  "password": "Guest123!@#",
  "nickname": "길동",
  "phone": "01012345678",
  "role": "GUEST",
  "businessNumber": null
}

### 로그인 요청 - 손님
# @no-redirect
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "guest@example.com",
  "password": "Guest123!@#"
}

